<pre><code>class Overflowtest {    public static void main(String[] args) {      byte maxValue= Byte.MAX_VALUE;     System.out.println("maxValue of byte is "+maxValue);     System.out.println("add 1 to maxValue of byte is "+maxValue+(byte)2);    } } </code></pre>  <p>Why there is no overflow happened when I try <code>maxValue+(byte)2</code>? But if I did this, <code>(byte)(maxValue+2)</code>, overflow happened. </p>